#: ../../unions.md:1
msgid "Union values"
msgstr "联合值"

#: ../../unions.md:3
msgid "*New in Koffi 2.5*"
msgstr "*Koffi 2.5*引入"

#: ../../unions.md:5
msgid "Union definition"
msgstr "定义联合"

#: ../../unions.md:7
msgid ""
"You can declare unions with a syntax similar to structs, but with the "
"`koffi.union()` function. This function takes two arguments: the first "
"one is the name of the type, and the second one is an object containing "
"the union member names and types. You can omit the first argument to "
"declare an anonymous union."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用`koffi.union()`函数声明联合, 类似struct的语法. "
"这个函数接受两个参数, 前者是类型的名称, 后者是一个含有联合成员名称和类型的对象. "
"你可以省略第一个参数来声明一个匿名联合."

#: ../../unions.md:9
msgid ""
"The following example illustrates how to declare the same union in C and "
"in JS with Koffi:"
msgstr ""
"下面的例子展示了如何在C和用Koffi在JS中声明相同的联合."

#: ../../unions.md:25
msgid "Input unions"
msgstr "输入联合"

#: ../../unions.md:27
msgid "Passing union values to C"
msgstr "传递联合值到C"

#: ../../unions.md:29
msgid ""
"You can instantiate an union object with `koffi.Union(type)`. This will "
"create a special object that contains at most one active member."
msgstr ""
"你可以通过`Koffi.Union(type)`来实例化一个联合对象. 这会构造一个特殊的对象, 包含至多一个激活的成员."

#: ../../unions.md:31
msgid ""
"Once you have created an instance of your union, you can simply set the "
"member with the dot operator as you would with a basic object. Then, "
"simply pass your union value to the C function you wish."
msgstr ""
"当你构造了一个你的联合的示例之后, 你可以简单的通过点运算符设置成员, 就像你对普通对象做的一样. "
"然后, 简单的将你的联合值传递给你希望的C函数."

#: ../../unions.md:45
msgid ""
"For simplicity, Koffi also accepts object literals with one property (no "
"more, no less) setting the corresponding union member. The example belows"
" uses this to simplify the code shown above:"
msgstr ""
"为了更加简便, Koffi也接受用含有单个属性(不多不少)的字面量对象来设置对应的联合成员(译注:联合参数). 下面的例子使用这个方法简化了上面的代码:"

#: ../../unions.md:56
msgid "Win32 example"
msgstr "Win32示例"

#: ../../unions.md:58
msgid ""
"The following example uses the [SendInput](https://learn.microsoft.com"
"/en-us/windows/win32/api/winuser/nf-winuser-sendinput) Win32 API to emit "
"the Win+D shortcut and hide windows (show the desktop)."
msgstr ""
"下面的例子使用了[SendInput](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/api/winuser/nf-winuser-sendinput)这一Win32 API"
"生成Win+D快捷键来隐藏窗口(显示桌面)."

#: ../../unions.md:141
msgid "Output unions"
msgstr "输出联合"

#: ../../unions.md:143
msgid ""
"Unlike structs, Koffi does not know which union member is valid, and it "
"cannot decode it automatically. You can however use special `koffi.Union`"
" objects for output parameters, and decode the memory after the call."
msgstr ""
"不同于结构体, Koffi不知道哪个联合成员是激活的, 因此它不能自动将其解码. 然而你可以使用特殊的`koffi.Union`对象作为输出参数, "
"然后在调用结束后解码内存."

#: ../../unions.md:145
msgid ""
"To decode an output union pointer parameter, create a placeholder object "
"with `new koffi.Union(type)` and pass the resulting object to the "
"function."
msgstr ""
"要解码一个输出联合指针参数, 使用`new koffi.Union(type)`构造一个占位对象然后将其传递给函数."

#: ../../unions.md:147
msgid ""
"After the call, you can dereference the member value you want on this "
"object and Koffi will decode it at this moment."
msgstr ""
"调用结束后, 你可以解引用这个对象中你想要的成员, Koffi会在此时解码它."

#: ../../unions.md:149
msgid ""
"The following example illustrates the use of `koffi.Union()` to decode "
"output unions after the call."
msgstr ""
"下面的例子展示了在函数调用后使用`koffi.Union()`解码输出联合."

